@startuml
autonumber
actor User
participant "CVParser" as CVParser
participant "CVViewer" as CVViewer
participant "ScreeningQuestionManager" as ScreeningQuestionManager
participant "RatingEngine" as RatingEngine
participant "Database" as Database
participant "APIGateway" as APIGateway
participant "Security" as Security
APIGateway ->> Security : Authenticate incoming request
Security ->> APIGateway : Authorize authenticated request
APIGateway ->> CVParser : Parse and analyze submitted CV
CVParser ->> CVViewer : Display parsed CV to applicant
APIGateway ->> ScreeningQuestionManager : Retrieve and present screening questions
ScreeningQuestionManager ->> CVViewer : Present screening questions to applicant
APIGateway ->> RatingEngine : Generate rating based on parsed CV
RatingEngine ->> Database : Store generated rating
Database ->> APIGateway : Retrieve stored rating
APIGateway ->> Security : Authorize access to stored rating
@enduml